title: swayzak - himawari  (2000)
description:
This is a great album from swayzak, who are based around trance / electronica and this album features some interesting material of various electronical music styles.



himawari features many smooth and vibrant rhythmic melodies combined with some great beats, making it a very welcome addition to any sort of trance music collection.



the music files are encoded in mp3 320kbps format for high sound playback and optimum performance through devices ranging from portable media players to hi-fi sound systems.



Seed well and enjoy!
